      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KING FEARLESS (8) pinged the lids and was in the firing line early but drifted out of it when 6th at this track in Grade 5 company. Solid record here at the distance winning eight races. Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and two minor placings from eight starts. Has ability and looks hard to stop. SPLIT VISION (1) has missed the frame at his last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when second (19.78) at this track in a Other. Speedy runner and should be in the action early from the inside. Well placed here and can atone this time. RIPPIN' PEDRO (5) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (19.95) from Box 3 at this track. Has good box speed and can overcome the tricky draw. Can feature again. ASTON BIDEN (2) was in the money last start here at this trip - likely to feature again.",
